graph TD
    User((User)) -->|Voice/Text| WS[WebSocket Server - FastAPI]
    WS -->|Audio Chunks| STT[Deepgram STT]
    STT -->|Transcript| Agent[LLM Agent - GPT-4o-mini]
    
    subgraph Memory
        Session[Redis Session Context]
        Persistent[Redis Patient History]
    end
    
    Agent <--> Session
    Agent <--> Persistent
    
    subgraph Tools
        AppLogic[Appointment Engine]
        DB[(SQLite/Postgres)]
    end
    
    Agent -->|Tool Call| AppLogic
    AppLogic --> DB
    
    Agent -->|Response Text| TTS[Deepgram TTS - Aura]
    TTS -->|Audio Stream| WS
    WS -->|Audio/Metrics| User
    
    style WS fill:#4f46e5,color:#fff
    style Agent fill:#22d3ee,color:#000
    style Memory fill:#facc15,color:#000
